MORE(1)

NAME
    more - page a file or standard input

SYNOPSIS
    more [path]

DESCRIPTION
    more displays text one screen at a time. With path, it reads that file.
    Without path, it reads standard input.

PAGER KEYS
    Enter
        Advance one line.

    q
    Q
        Quit.

    any other key
        Clear the screen and advance one page.

EXAMPLES
    more /var/log/boot.txt
    cat /var/log/boot.txt | more

SEE ALSO
    cat(1), man(1)
